item.title: CVE-2023-1478|2023-04-10T13:17:59.068Z -- unknown -- hummingbird
item.description: The Hummingbird WordPress plugin before 3.4.2 does not validate the generated file path for page cache files before writing them, leading to a path traversal vulnerability in the page cache module.
